# 🚀 DevTinder

DevTinder is a full-stack developer networking platform that allows developers to connect, interact, and collaborate based on their skills and interests.

---

## 🌟 Features

### 👤 User
- User authentication (Signup/Login)
- Create and update developer profile
- View other developers
- Send connection requests
- Accept/Reject requests

### 🔗 Networking
- Match developers based on skills/interests
- View connections
- Explore new developers

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- CSS3

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### Database
- MongoDB (Mongoose)

### Authentication
- JWT (JSON Web Tokens)

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 🔹 Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/divyanshuraj1095/DevTinder.git
cd DevTinder

🔧 Backend Setup
cd backend
npm install

🌐 Environment Variables
Backend
PORT
MONGO_URI
JWT_SECRET

Frontend
VITE_BACKEND_URL

Run backend:
npm run dev (nodemon)

